|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Here's how you can grant `VIEW DEFINITION` for all objects in the database:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```sql                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | USE [YourDatabaseName];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GO                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GRANT VIEW DEFINITION ON DATABASE::[YourDatabaseName] TO [UserName];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GO                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Replace `[YourDatabaseName]` and `[UserName]` with the appropriate names for your setup.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | If you only want to grant permission for all views and not other objects, you'll need to script this out using a loop or cursor for each view in the database. Here's a basic example using a cursor:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```sql                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | USE [YourDatabaseName];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GO                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | DECLARE @ViewName NVARCHAR(500)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | DECLARE view_cursor CURSOR FOR                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | SELECT '[' + TABLE_SCHEMA + '].[' + TABLE_NAME + ']'                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.VIEWS                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | OPEN view_cursor                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | FETCH NEXT FROM view_cursor INTO @ViewName                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | BEGIN                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     EXEC('GRANT VIEW DEFINITION ON ' + @ViewName + ' TO [UserName]')                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     FETCH NEXT FROM view_cursor INTO @ViewName                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | END                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | CLOSE view_cursor                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | DEALLOCATE view_cursor                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GO                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Here's how you can revoke the `VIEW DEFINITION` permission for the entire database:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```sql                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | USE [YourDatabaseName];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GO                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | REVOKE VIEW DEFINITION ON DATABASE::[YourDatabaseName] FROM [UserName];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | GO                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Replace `[YourDatabaseName]` and `[UserName]` with the appropriate names for your setup.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | This will remove the `VIEW DEFINITION` permission for the user on all objects in the database. If there were any specific objects (like certain views or tables) where the user had `VIEW DEFINITION` permission granted individually, those permissions would remain. If you want to ensure the user doesn't have `VIEW DEFINITION` on any object in the database, you'd have to revoke it for each object separately.                              |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | **Step-by-step guide:**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **Initialize a Git repository in your workspace**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Before you link your local workspace with the GitLab project, ensure that your workspace has a git repository initialized. If it's not initialized yet, do so by:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    cd path/to/your/workspace                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git init                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Add your files to the git repository**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you have files already in your workspace, you can add them to your git repository:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git add .                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git commit -m "Initial commit"                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Link your local repository with your GitLab project**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    In your GitLab project, you should see a page where it gives you instructions to push an existing repository. If you have an empty project, the URL you need will be something like `git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud:username/projectname.git` (replace `username` and `projectname` accordingly).                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Add this URL as the 'origin' for your local repository:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git remote add origin git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud:username/projectname.git                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you mistakenly added the wrong URL or need to change it later, you can do so using:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git remote set-url origin git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud:username/projectname.git                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. **Push your commits to the GitLab project**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git push -u origin master                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    (Replace `master` with `main` or whichever branch name you're using if it's different.)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 5. **Using Git in VSCode**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - With your workspace open in VSCode, if you haven't installed it yet, install the built-in Git extension.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Go to the Source Control view by clicking on the branch icon in the sidebar or press `Ctrl + Shift + G`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - You should now see your changes, commits, branches, etc. You can commit and push directly from VSCode. If there are any changes, they will show up in this pane. You can then stage, commit, and push/pull changes all within VSCode.                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 6. **Additional Considerations**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Ensure that your SSH key is correctly loaded into your SSH agent, especially if you have multiple keys or if you restarted your computer. Use `ssh-add` to add your key to the agent if needed.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - If there's a problem with the connection, you can test your SSH connection to GitLab with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ssh -T git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      It should welcome you.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | That's all! With these steps, your local workspace in VSCode should be linked to your GitLab project, and you can leverage the power of Git within VSCode.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
