|    |                                      |               |               | To resolve this issue, follow these steps:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **Pull the remote changes first**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Before merging, it's always a good idea to make sure you know what changes are coming from the remote repository. First, fetch the changes without merging:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git fetch origin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Merge or Rebase**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Merge**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      Merging will create a new commit in your local branch that combines the changes.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      git merge origin/master                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      If there are any merge conflicts, you'll need to resolve them. Once resolved, continue with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      git commit                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Rebase** (Alternative to Merge):                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      Rebasing is another way to integrate changes. Instead of creating a merge commit, rebasing will "replay" your local changes on top of the remote changes.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      git rebase origin/master                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      Again, if there are conflicts, resolve them, and then continue the rebase with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      git rebase --continue                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |      ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Push your changes**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Now that your local branch is updated with remote changes, you can push your changes:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git push -u origin master                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Going forward, always remember to `pull` changes from the remote repository before pushing new changes, especially if there are multiple people working on the project or if you're making changes directly on GitLab (e.g., editing files or committing via the web interface).                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    The GitLab Workflow extension integrates GitLab's features into VSCode. |    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |    - After installation, you might need to configure your GitLab token in the settings for a more integrated experience.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 5. **Working with the Repository**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

Stage the changes by clicking on the `+` sign next to each file.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |    - Push the changes to GitLab with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git push                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 6. **Fetching Updates from GitLab**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If there are updates on GitLab that you want to fetch, or if you're collaborating with others, it's a good idea to pull in updates frequently.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git pull                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 7. **Branching and Merging**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you want to work on features separately, you can use branches.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - To create a new branch and switch to it:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git checkout -b new_feature_name                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - To switch between branches:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git checkout other_branch_name                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - After completing your feature and committing all changes, you can merge it back to the main branch (assuming it's named `master`):                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git checkout master                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git merge new_feature_name                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 8. **Pushing and Pull Requests**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you're working in a team or need someone to review your changes, you can create a merge request (known as pull request in GitHub terminology).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    After pushing your branch to GitLab:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git push -u origin new_feature_name                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Go to the GitLab web interface, navigate to your project, and you'll see a prompt to create a new merge request for your branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Remember, these are basic Git and GitLab operations. Depending on your workflow, there are many advanced features and operations you can perform. The above should get you started with integrating VSCode and GitLab.                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
