|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Here's how to troubleshoot and resolve the issue:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **Check SSH Agent & Key**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    The SSH agent should be running, and your key should be added to it. You can check this by:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ssh-add -l                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If your key is not listed, add it:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ssh-add path_to_your_private_key                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    For default key locations, simply:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ssh-add                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Verify SSH Key Pair**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Ensure that the public key you've added to GitLab (usually `~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub`) corresponds to the private key on your local machine (`~/.ssh/id_rsa` or whatever name/path you've given).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Test GitLab SSH Connection**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Test your connection to GitLab using SSH:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ssh -T git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    You should receive a welcome message. If you receive the same "Permission denied" message, it indicates that your SSH key isn't set up correctly on the GitLab server.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. **Check Repository URL**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Make sure you're pushing to the correct repository. You can check the remote URL with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git remote -v                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If the URL is incorrect or not what you expected, you can change it with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    git remote set-url origin your_correct_repository_url                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 5. **Repository Access**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Ensure that you have write access to the GitLab repository. If you don't own the repository, request the owner to give you the necessary permissions.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 6. **Check Repository Existence**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Ensure that the repository you're trying to push to actually exists on the GitLab server.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 7. **Firewall or Network Issues**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you're behind a firewall or using a VPN, it might be blocking your SSH connection to GitLab. Ensure that port 22 (standard SSH port) is open and accessible.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 8. **Re-Add SSH Key to GitLab**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    As a last resort, try removing and re-adding your SSH key to GitLab:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Log in to GitLab.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Navigate to your profile settings.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Go to SSH Keys.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Remove the existing SSH key.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Add it again.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | If you've gone through all these steps and still face the issue, consider reaching out to your GitLab server administrator or seeking further technical support, as the problem could be on the server-side or require deeper network diagnostics.                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               | Here's how to troubleshoot and resolve this on a Windows machine:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **Start SSH Agent**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Before you can add your SSH key, the SSH agent needs to be running.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```powershell                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    # Start the ssh-agent in the background                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    eval $(ssh-agent -s)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    You should see something like `Agent pid 12345` as output. This means the agent has started.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Add Your SSH Key**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Once the SSH agent is running, you can add your SSH key.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```powershell                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ssh-add C:\Users\IBRAHHO\.ssh\id_gitlab                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Ensure you provide the correct path to your private SSH key if it's different from the above.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Persistent SSH Agent Across Terminal Sessions**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you don't want to start the SSH agent every time you open a new terminal session, consider adding the `ssh-agent` start command to your shell's startup script (like `.bashrc`, `.zshrc`, or equivalent for your shell).                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. **For Windows Native SSH (Optional)**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    If you're using the SSH client that's built into Windows (not through Git Bash or another tool), you might have to manage your keys using the Windows-native tools.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Open a command prompt as an administrator.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Run `ssh-agent` to ensure it's running.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Add your key using `ssh-add`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | **Note**: If you installed Git for Windows, it comes with a program called Git Bash. This provides a Bash-like terminal and includes many UNIX utilities, including `ssh` and `ssh-add`. If you're using Git Bash and the standard commands aren't working, ensure you're in the right environment and the SSH tools are available.                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
