|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     a. **Create a Personal Access Token**: If you don’t have one, you can create a personal access token by going to your GitLab:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |        - Profile > Settings > Access Tokens                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |        - Create a new token with the `api` scope.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |        - Copy the token after creation as it won't be shown again.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     b. **Use the Token**: When git asks for a password, use the personal access token as the password.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Update Cached Credentials**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     - **On macOS**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |       1. Open the Keychain Access app.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |       2. In the search, look for `gitlab`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |       3. Find the entry corresponding to your GitLab instance and update the password or delete the entry to be prompted again.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     - **On Windows**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |       1. Open the Control Panel.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |       2. Go to User Accounts > Credential Manager.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |       3. Look for an entry that matches your GitLab instance and update or delete it.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     - **On Linux**: It depends on how credentials are cached. If you use a credential helper, check the documentation for it. If you don't use a helper, you might be asked for your credentials every time.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. **HTTPS to SSH**: If you're comfortable using SSH keys, consider switching from HTTPS to SSH for your repository's remote. SSH keys can provide a more seamless authentication experience. However, this would require you to have SSH keys set up on your machine and added to your GitLab account.                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 5. **Check URL**: Ensure the repository URL is correct. If you've copied the URL from somewhere, ensure there are no extra spaces or characters.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 6. **Proxy or VPN Issues**: If you're behind a proxy or VPN, they can sometimes interfere with Git operations. Ensure you have the necessary configurations set up or try momentarily disabling them to see if that's the cause.                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 7. **Contact Support**: If none of the above solutions work, it might be a good idea to reach out to your organization's IT or the support team of your GitLab instance for help.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Remember to never share your personal access tokens, SSH keys, or passwords with others, including here.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | To address this:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **View Existing Remotes**: Before making any changes, check your current remote configurations:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git remote -v                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    This will show you the URLs of remotes you have linked with your local repository.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Change the URL for an Existing Remote**: If you want to modify the URL of the `origin` to the new one:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git remote set-url origin git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud:testing_vscode/test_vscode.git                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Remove and Re-add the Remote**: Another method is to remove the `origin` and then add it again with the new URL. However, this approach is essentially equivalent to the `set-url` command, so there's generally no need to do it this way unless you're troubleshooting:                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git remote remove origin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git remote add origin git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud:testing_vscode/test_vscode.git                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. **Add with a Different Name**: If for some reason you want to keep the old `origin` and add the new URL as a different remote, you can do so:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git remote add newRemoteName git@gitlab.hlag.altemista.cloud:testing_vscode/test_vscode.git                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Replace `newRemoteName` with whatever name you want to give to the new remote. Later, when you push or pull, you'll need to specify this remote name.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | After making your desired changes, you can use `git remote -v` again to ensure your remotes are configured as you want them.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
