|    |                                      |               |               | # Git Commands Guide                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## Getting & Creating Projects                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git init`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Initialize a local Git repository.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git init [repository name]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git clone [url]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Download a project and its entire version history.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git clone [https://github.com/user/repository.git]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## Configuration                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git config --global user.name "[name]"`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Set author name for all repositories.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git config --global user.name "John Doe"`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git config --global user.email "[email address]"`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Set author email for all repositories.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git config --global user.email "john@example.com"`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## Local Changes                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git status`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: List changes in your working directory.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git add [file]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Add changes from specific file to staging area.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git add example.txt`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. `git commit -m "[descriptive message]"`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Record changes to the repository.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git commit -m "Fixed bug in the application"`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## Branching & Merging                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git branch`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: List all branches in your repo, and also tell you what branch you're currently in.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git branch -a`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: List all branches in your repo, including those from remote.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. `git branch [branch-name]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Create a new branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git branch feature/new-feature`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. `git checkout [branch-name]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Switch to a different branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git checkout feature/new-feature`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 5. `git merge [branch]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Merge specified branch into the current branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## Sharing & Updating                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git push [alias] [branch]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Upload local branch commits to GitHub.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git push origin master`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git pull`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Download changes and directly merge/integrate into HEAD.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## Inspecting & Comparing                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git log`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Show commit logs.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git diff [source branch] [target branch]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: View changes between two branches.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `git diff master feature/new-feature`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | Remember, this is a basic guide. Git has a lot more commands and options, so it's a good idea to refer to the [official documentation](https://git-scm.com/docs) or use `git help [command]` for more detailed information on each command.                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
