|    |                                      |               |               | ### GitLab Merge Requests:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `git checkout -b feature-branch`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Create and switch to a new feature branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `git checkout -b my-feature`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `git push origin feature-branch`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Push the new feature branch to GitLab.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `git push origin my-feature`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. In the GitLab UI:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Go to **Merge Requests** → **New Merge Request** and select your `feature-branch` to create a new merge request.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ### GitLab CI/CD:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `gitlab-runner exec [executor] [.gitlab-ci.yml job]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Execute a GitLab CI job locally using GitLab runner (helpful for debugging).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gitlab-runner exec shell test_job`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: If you have a `.gitlab-ci.yml` job named `test_job`, run it locally with the shell executor.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ## GitHub Commands:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. `gh auth login`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Authenticate with a GitHub instance.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: Follow the interactive prompts after running the command.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. `gh issue list`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: List and filter issues in a repository.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh issue list`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. `gh issue view [issue_number]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: View an issue in the browser or terminal.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gh issue view 123`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh issue view 456`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. `gh issue create`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Create a new issue.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: Follow the interactive prompts after running the command.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 5. `gh pr list`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: List and filter pull requests in a repository.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh pr list`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 6. `gh pr view [pr_number]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: View a pull request in the browser or terminal.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gh pr view 123`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh pr view 456`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 7. `gh pr create`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Create a new pull request.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: Follow the interactive prompts after running the command.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 8. `gh pr checkout [pr_number]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Check out a pull request locally.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gh pr checkout 123`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh pr checkout 456`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 9. `gh gist create [file...]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Create a new GitHub gist.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gh gist create hello.py`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh gist create script.js`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 10. `gh gist list`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: List your gists.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh gist list`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 11. `gh repo create [name]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Create a new repository on GitHub.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gh repo create my-new-repo`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh repo create awesome-project`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 12. `gh repo fork [repository]`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Description**: Fork an existing repository.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Usage**: `gh repo fork user/repo`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - **Example**: `gh repo fork octocat/demo`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **Ensure LFS is Initialized**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     If you haven't initialized LFS for your repository, you can do so with:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git lfs install                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Track Large Files**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     Before adding the large files, you need to specify which files should be tracked by LFS. For example, if you want LFS to track `.mp4` files, you can run:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git lfs track "*.mp4"                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Recommit Large Files**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     Since you've already added and committed the large files without LFS tracking, you'll need to recommit them.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     First, remove the large files from the repository (this doesn't delete them from your disk, just from Git's tracking):                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git rm --cached path/to/your/file.mp4                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     Then, re-add them:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git add path/to/your/file.mp4                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     And then, commit:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git commit -m "Add large files with LFS"                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 4. **Push Again**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     Try pushing to GitHub again:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     git push origin main                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | After doing the above, your push should work without the file size errors, as the large files will be correctly managed by Git LFS.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               | 1. **Check the Unmerged Files**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Use the following command to see the list of files with merge conflicts:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 2. **Resolve the Conflicts**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Open the files with merge conflicts (as indicated in the `git status` output). You'll see conflict markers (`<<<<<<<`, `=======`, and `>>>>>>>`). These markers delineate the differences between the branches that are conflicting.                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Everything between `<<<<<<<` and `=======` is what's in your current branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    - Everything between `=======` and `>>>>>>>` is what's in the conflicting branch.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    Manually resolve the conflicts by editing the files. Once resolved, save the files.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | 3. **Mark the Conflicts as Resolved**:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    After manually resolving the conflicts in the files, you'll need to mark them as resolved with the following command:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |    ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |    git rebase --continue                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                             groupby_columns: List[str],                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
