|    |                                      |               |               |     """                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     Filter dataframe to only include rows with the latest timestamp based on groupby columns.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param df: Input DataFrame.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param groupby_columns: Columns to group by.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param timestamp_column: Column that holds the timestamp.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param filters: List of tuples where each tuple is (column, operator, value) to filter df.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                     Example: [("client", "=", "1"), ("id_number", "!=", "100")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :return: Filtered DataFrame.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     """                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     # Apply filters                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     for column, operator, value in filters:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         if operator == "=":                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |             df = df.filter(df[column] == value)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         elif operator == "!=":                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |             df = df.filter(df[column] != value)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         elif operator == ">":                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |             df = df.filter(df[column] > value)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         elif operator == "<":                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |             df = df.filter(df[column] < value)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         elif operator == ">=":                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |             df = df.filter(df[column] >= value)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         elif operator == "<=":                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |             df = df.filter(df[column] <= value)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |         # You can continue adding more operators as needed                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     # Get max timestamp for groupby_columns                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     max_timestamp = df.groupBy(*groupby_columns).agg(F.max(timestamp_column).alias("Max_Timestamp"))                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |     join_conditions = [df[col] == max_timestamp[col] for col in groupby_columns] + [df[timestamp_column] == max_timestamp["Max_Timestamp"]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     df_result = df.join(max_timestamp, on=join_conditions, how='inner')\                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               | Here's a function named `join_dataframes`:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```python                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | from pyspark.sql import DataFrame                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | from typing import List, Tuple                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | def join_dataframes(df1: DataFrame, df2: DataFrame, join_type: str, join_columns: List[Tuple[str, str]]) -> DataFrame:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     """                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     Join two dataframes based on specified columns and join type.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param df1: First DataFrame.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param df2: Second DataFrame.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param join_type: Type of join (e.g., 'inner', 'left', 'right', etc.).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :param join_columns: List of tuples specifying join columns for df1 and df2.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                          Each tuple is (df1_column, df2_column).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     :return: Joined DataFrame.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     """                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     join_conditions = [df1[col1] == df2[col2] for col1, col2 in join_columns]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |     return df1.join(df2, on=join_conditions, how=join_type)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | # Example Usage:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |

|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | joined_df = join_dataframes(filtered_df, tf_tt1190, 'inner', [('client', 'customer'), ('id_number', 'id_number')])                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | joined_df.show()                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               | ```                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                       |                                      |
|    |                                      |               |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |                       |                                      |
